      <div class="subfield"><strong>$b - Geographic classification subarea code</strong> <div class="description">Geographic subarea code related to the geographic area coded in subfield $a. </div>
         <div class="description2">
            <div class="description">Each geographic subarea code is contained in a separate subfield $b.
                                 Subfield $b may be repeated for subareas falling within a main area
                                 with the same code.
            </div>
         </div>
