      <div class="subfield"><strong>$d - Populated place name</strong> <div class="description">Approved form of name for a populated place.</div>
         <div class="description2">
            <div class="description">In the case of a name established by the U.S. Board on Geographic Names, if a
                                 short form of the name has been approved, that form is used in preference to the
                                 full form of name.
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="example">
